cs.SI, cs.SOC, cs.IR, cs.CYBER, cs.DL 

The paper discusses the use of digital traces to map knowledge across the world, which falls under the categories of social media analysis, information retrieval, cybersecurity, and deep learning. Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.SOC (Computational Social Science), followed by cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.CYBER (Cybersecurity), and cs.DL (Deep Learning).
